Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 19/8/2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to HelperAssistant. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share your information when you interact with our bot.

2. Information We Collect

Personal Information: We do not collect personally identifiable information (PII) such as your name, email address, or phone number unless you voluntarily provide it during interactions.
Usage Data: We collect data on how you use the bot, including interactions, commands, and feedback. This helps us understand user behavior and improve our services.
Device and Technical Information: We may collect information about the device and software you use to interact with the bot, such as IP address, browser type, and operating system.
3. How We Use Your Information

To Provide and Improve Services: We use your information to enhance the bot's functionality, fix issues, and deliver a better user experience.
For Communication: If you provide contact information, we may use it to communicate with you regarding updates, support, or changes to our services.
Analytics and Research: We analyze usage data to understand trends and improve the bot's performance.
4. Data Sharing and Disclosure

Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in operating the bot or providing services to you. These parties are bound by confidentiality agreements.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law or to protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property.
5. Data Security

We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. However, no data transmission over the internet can be guaranteed to be completely secure.

6. User Rights

Access and Correction: You may request access to the information we hold about you and request corrections if necessary.
Opt-Out: If you wish to stop receiving communications from us, you can opt-out by [describe opt-out method].
7. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated policy on our platform. Your continued use of the bot constitutes your acceptance of the revised policy.

